response.original_title: รุ่นพี่(คน)โปรด
response.overview: Unfortunately for Pim, she has captured the attention of her school's resident bully clique. After being bullied for over a year, however, things start to look up. Prot, the hottest girl in school, steps in to rescue her from her bullies. Not only that, but she continues to do so. All the time they're spending together... is it all just to keep Pim safe, or could there be feelings involved?
response.title: Run Phi (Khon) Prot
